title: Katie Rodan + Kathy Fields: Serial Skin-Care Entrepreneurs
description: Katie Rodan and Kathy Fields, co-founders of skincare treatment Proactiv and their namesake brand, Rodan + Fields, tell WSJ's Veronica Dagher what they've learned about partnership and building companies.
